data.description: Welcome to 16902 Lawton rd. This beautiful home has everything you need and so much more. This 2200+sqft home boasts a very open floor plan with 2 master suites and an office that can very easily be a 3rd room. As you sit on your front porch and take in the endless views you realize what peace really is. Its large 3 car garage has plenty of room for all your toys and is also equipped with its own bathroom. There is another garage that has been turned into an amazing workshop. With the solar grid your power bill is less than $30 per month and your own personal well allows you to have all the water you need.
